    <div class="lg:col-span-2 p-8 sm:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center border-b-2 lg:border-b-0 lg:border-r-2 border-web5-dark">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">
        No bait-and-switch, no hidden relay, no "it's decentralized enough."
      </h3>
